description: CITY POINT CONDO with HUGE ROOFTOP DECK!!!!  These views are a MUST SEE!! This condo is located in City Point, on the eastern end of South Boston with Castle Island to the east.  The home is on conveniently located on the second floor.  The oversized windows splash sun into the large living room with wood burning fireplace.  There is also an office area off the family room with a large window looking out the front of the condo.(room for a single bed)  The bedroom is large allowing for a king size bed, closet and a separate closet for laundry units in the bedroom. The kitchen has a refrigerator, range, dishwasher and microwave with lots of cabinet space.  The full bath has a tub/shower and a hall closet just outside for linens etc.  HOA, only $218, includes Heat, Water & Sewer!!!  Take the steps up the backside of the condo to one of the Largest Rooftop Decks in South Boston with views of the Boston Skyline & Ocean!!! Welcome Home!!!
